Functional Interfaces 
- Functional interface which contains only SAM
- SAM Means "Single Abstract Method"
-In functional Interface we can have static,default, and private methods also.
Ex: java.util.function- all interfaces from this package are functional Interfaces.

Lamda Expressions
-The main objective of Lambda expression is :to Bring functional programming into java .
-It is an Anonymous(Name less) function in Java.
-What is Anonymous? It means Nameless, without return type and without access modifier.

